1
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:32,560
Do you know where you went wrong?

2
00:01:33,439 --> 00:01:33,920
Imperial Father.

3
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:35,040
Your child...

4
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:36,599
Your child was careless for a moment

5
00:01:37,079 --> 00:01:38,799
and fell into a scheming man's trap.

6
00:01:38,959 --> 00:01:39,519
Your child deserves punishment.

7
00:01:39,719 --> 00:01:40,280
Your child deserves punishment.

8
00:01:40,480 --> 00:01:41,719
Your child deserves punishment.

9
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,480
Your child deserves punishment.

10
00:01:43,719 --> 00:01:45,280
Your child deserves punishment.

11
00:01:46,159 --> 00:01:46,840
Crown Prince.

12
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:49,000
You strayed onto the wrong path

13
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:51,200
only because you harbored evil thoughts.

14
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:54,599
Hence your deal with the Left Chancellor.

15
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:58,200
Your... Your child knows his fault.

16
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,799
Your child knows his fault.

17
00:02:00,239 --> 00:02:01,200
Confined to the Eastern Palace.

18
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:02,719
Reflect on your wrongs for half a year.

19
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,280
Repent thoroughly.

20
00:02:06,799 --> 00:02:07,719
Thank you, Imperial Father.

21
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:09,439
You may leave.

22
00:02:27,759 --> 00:02:28,439
Geng Jing.

23
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:43,360
Reporting to Your Majesty.

24
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:44,719
Your subject has submitted the evidence

25
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:46,439
of the Empress and Left Chancellor's plot

26
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:47,840
to the Supreme Court.

27
00:02:48,599 --> 00:02:49,319
Well done.

28
00:02:49,919 --> 00:02:50,439
Geng Jing.

29
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:52,719
These years undercover

30
00:02:53,319 --> 00:02:54,240
must have been hard on you.

31
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:08,439
You...

32
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:10,759
Old Pan.

33
00:03:12,479 --> 00:03:13,400
I should have known it was you.

34
00:03:14,319 --> 00:03:14,879
That's right.

35
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:18,199
I was the Empress's mole
in the Imperial Inspectorate,

36
00:03:20,879 --> 00:03:22,319
but it was all arranged by His Majesty.

37
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:25,280
I...

38
00:03:34,639 --> 00:03:35,240
Ning Chen.

39
00:03:35,879 --> 00:03:37,039
You must have already guessed.

40
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:39,039
To put the Third Prince on the throne,
the Left Chancellor

41
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,960
even took poison himself
to frame the Crown Prince.

42
00:03:41,639 --> 00:03:43,080
Fortunately, His Majesty was prepared.

43
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,599
This was also a test for you.

44
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:48,560
Ning Chen truly did not disappoint Us.

45
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,599
The rest of you, leave us.

46
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:53,000
We wish to speak with Ning Chen alone.

47
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,719
Your subject takes leave.

48
00:04:00,599 --> 00:04:01,319
Ning Chen.

49
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:02,759
This battle,

50
00:04:03,599 --> 00:04:05,240
you handled beautifully.

51
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:09,000
It's nothing compared to Your Majesty.

52
00:04:11,159 --> 00:04:12,560
You're blaming Us.

53
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:14,120
Your subject would not dare.

54
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:20,480
We bear the safety of the Great Xuan realm,

55
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:22,879
the livelihood of all the people,

56
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:24,000
day after day,

57
00:04:24,279 --> 00:04:26,959
handling endless piles of memorials.

58
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:27,879
For Our entire life,

59
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:31,519
We must be locked within this deep palace.

60
00:04:32,759 --> 00:04:33,439
We...

61
00:04:36,160 --> 00:04:38,959
honestly envy you sometimes.

62
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:42,240
You can do as you please,

63
00:04:43,519 --> 00:04:45,279
neither humble nor arrogant.

64
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:47,319
Your subject confesses his guilt.

65
00:04:49,079 --> 00:04:49,879
You...

66
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,920
Seeing you like this,

67
00:04:52,279 --> 00:04:54,800
We're rather not used to it.

68
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:55,439
Speak.

69
00:04:55,959 --> 00:04:57,959
You've rendered great service once again.

70
00:04:58,600 --> 00:04:59,879
What reward do you wish for?

71
00:05:00,759 --> 00:05:01,480
Your subject...

72
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:05,079
What if We betroth Huaian to you,

73
00:05:05,519 --> 00:05:07,480
placing you among the imperial family?

74
00:05:08,079 --> 00:05:09,519
Are you willing

75
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:12,600
to become Our son?

76
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:14,279
Your subject

77
00:05:15,199 --> 00:05:16,839
is unworthy.

78
00:05:17,439 --> 00:05:18,160
You are worthy.

79
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:20,120
Have We not said it before?

80
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:22,319
The Crown Prince's seat
belongs to the worthy.

81
00:05:22,639 --> 00:05:24,199
And with your abilities,

82
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:25,439
entrusting Great Xuan to you,

83
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:26,759
We are quite at ease.

84
00:05:28,519 --> 00:05:29,839
This old man is testing me.

85
00:05:30,279 --> 00:05:31,160
If I agree,

86
00:05:31,519 --> 00:05:32,680
won't I lose my life?

87
00:05:33,319 --> 00:05:34,800
These royal power struggles of yours

88
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:36,800
are truly terrifying.

89
00:05:37,079 --> 00:05:38,399
The Crown Prince loves the people
as his own.

90
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:39,560
He is benevolent and virtuous.

91
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:41,160
He is the best candidate.

92
00:05:41,439 --> 00:05:43,160
What virtue or ability
does your subject have?

93
00:05:43,519 --> 00:05:44,480
Your subject failed Your Majesty's grace.

94
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:46,000
I wish to lay down my arms and retire.

95
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:47,720
I beg Your Majesty to grant this.

96
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:52,480
You...

97
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,519
silly boy.

98
00:05:55,319 --> 00:05:57,240
Your subject has one more request.

99
00:05:57,439 --> 00:05:58,120
Speak.

100
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:00,560
Your subject humbly beseeches Your Majesty

101
00:06:00,759 --> 00:06:03,040
to free Yudie and Nanzhi
from the Music Bureau.

102
00:06:05,079 --> 00:06:07,040
Wasn't there already a Yudie?

103
00:06:07,199 --> 00:06:08,800
Now another one, Nanzhi?

104
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:11,360
So you're quite the philanderer.

105
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:12,079
No, it's not like that.

106
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:14,000
Yudie is indeed my beloved.

107
00:06:14,519 --> 00:06:15,439
As for Nanzhi,

108
00:06:17,279 --> 00:06:19,399
she's actually for a friend of mine.

109
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:22,639
On one side is friendship,

110
00:06:22,839 --> 00:06:24,160
on the other is love.

111
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:27,040
Very well, We grant your wish.

112
00:06:27,319 --> 00:06:28,639
But you must also promise Us

113
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:32,000
to remain at the Imperial Inspectorate

114
00:06:32,319 --> 00:06:34,639
and serve Great Xuan for life.

115
00:06:35,959 --> 00:06:36,959
This old man

116
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:39,240
still won't let me off.

117
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,639
What do you say?

118
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:44,399
Your subject will faithfully do his duty.

119
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,040
Now scram.

120
00:06:46,079 --> 00:06:46,720
Wait.

121
00:06:53,519 --> 00:06:54,959
We miss your poems.

122
00:06:55,399 --> 00:06:56,439
When you have free time,

123
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:58,480
write Us a few good ones.

124
00:06:59,199 --> 00:06:59,759
Piece of cake.

125
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:00,560
Go now.

126
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:27,959
My dear Ning.

127
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:29,519
Thank you.

128
00:07:31,199 --> 00:07:31,959
What are you saying?

129
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:35,040
Don't ever thank me again.

130
00:07:36,399 --> 00:07:37,360
I promised you

131
00:07:38,319 --> 00:07:39,680
I'd take you out of the Music Bureau.

132
00:07:49,959 --> 00:07:50,439
Chenzi!

133
00:07:50,839 --> 00:07:52,439
Slow down, will you? Chenzi!

134
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:53,439
Chenzi.

135
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:54,800
His Majesty has issued the edict.

136
00:07:55,519 --> 00:07:57,959
The two Ning brothers
are demoted to commoners,

137
00:07:58,079 --> 00:07:59,079
forever barred from office.

138
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:00,519
Ning Ziming and Chang Ruyue,

139
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:01,319
along with Ning Gan,

140
00:08:02,199 --> 00:08:02,959
will face Autumn Execution.

141
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:07,120
Many thanks, Brother Pan.

142
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,519
Let's drop the formalities.

143
00:08:09,079 --> 00:08:10,000
I should be the one thanking you.

144
00:08:10,399 --> 00:08:11,079
If it weren't for you,

145
00:08:12,759 --> 00:08:14,800
Nanzhi and I wouldn't be together.

146
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,199
I'm here.

147
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:18,759
My dear Pan.

148
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:20,000
Don't cry.

149
00:08:21,959 --> 00:08:23,560
I'll never let you leave me again.

150
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:27,879
Brother Ning, thank you.

151
00:08:29,319 --> 00:08:30,439
Stop with all this thanking.

152
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,399
It's such a nuisance.

153
00:08:36,399 --> 00:08:37,480
As for Yudie, don't even think about it.

154
00:08:37,639 --> 00:08:38,320
You just had to open your mouth, huh?

155
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,440
You've got a wife, easy for you to talk!

156
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:41,840
Look at all these happy couples,

157
00:08:47,799 --> 00:08:48,960
and I'm the only loner here.

158
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:50,960
Just ignore him.

159
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:52,519
Ladies,

160
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:54,120
got any single girlfriends?

161
00:08:54,639 --> 00:08:55,360
You, you, you...

162
00:08:56,279 --> 00:08:56,879
Brother Gao,

163
00:08:57,679 --> 00:08:58,879
I have a sister, Yu'er.

164
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:01,320
Virtuous and gentle, still unmarried.

165
00:09:01,679 --> 00:09:03,840
Want me to introduce you?

166
00:09:04,039 --> 00:09:04,440
Sure.

167
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:07,480
Sister,

168
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,200
you're such a good person.

169
00:09:10,399 --> 00:09:10,879
Get lost.

170
00:09:16,279 --> 00:09:16,919
Yu'er.

171
00:09:29,399 --> 00:09:30,960
Sister, I'm here.

172
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:33,159
Which gentleman requested me?

173
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:34,480
My dear sister,

174
00:09:36,559 --> 00:09:38,559
It's this Lord Gao.

175
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:40,240
Lord Gao.

176
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,279
Lord Gao is right here.

177
00:09:41,519 --> 00:09:42,600
I'm Lord Gao.

178
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:44,840
Lord Gao!

179
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,720
You really have unique taste.

180
00:09:46,799 --> 00:09:49,159
Look at your tall and mighty figure.

181
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:51,159
You must be a great hero.

182
00:09:55,399 --> 00:09:56,799
A big hippo. This won't work, right?

183
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:58,960
I think it works.

184
00:09:59,559 --> 00:10:00,320
This actually works?

185
00:10:01,360 --> 00:10:02,360
It really works.

186
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:07,600
My name is Jiang Yu'er.

187
00:10:07,879 --> 00:10:10,039
You can call me Little Er'er.

188
00:10:10,679 --> 00:10:11,720
My name is Gao Ziping.

189
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,320
My nickname is Little Qiu'qiu.

190
00:10:13,799 --> 00:10:15,279
You can call me Little Qiu'qiu.

191
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:18,360
Little Qiu'qiu.

192
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:19,559
Little Er'er.

193
00:10:19,679 --> 00:10:20,360
Little Qiu'qiu.

194
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:21,279
Little Er'er.

195
00:10:22,159 --> 00:10:23,320
My name is Little Cheng'cheng.

196
00:10:23,639 --> 00:10:25,120
The Princess has arrived!

197
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,600
Greetings, Princess.

198
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:44,279
She's your sweetheart from the Music Bureau?

199
00:10:44,759 --> 00:10:45,159
Yes.

200
00:10:45,759 --> 00:10:46,320
My dear Ning.

201
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:48,600
And this young lady is...

202
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:51,279
I am the Ninth Princess Huaian.

203
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:56,519
Your Highness.

204
00:10:57,039 --> 00:10:58,840
What are you...

205
00:10:59,559 --> 00:11:00,639
You like her that much?

206
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:01,399
Yes.

207
00:11:03,039 --> 00:11:04,200
Yudie is different from you.

208
00:11:05,039 --> 00:11:05,960
You have a noble status.

209
00:11:06,759 --> 00:11:08,279
But in this world, Yudie

210
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,120
only has me.

211
00:11:13,159 --> 00:11:14,080
From the time I was little,

212
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:16,120
whatever this princess sets her eyes on,

213
00:11:16,399 --> 00:11:17,480
I've always gotten it.

214
00:11:17,919 --> 00:11:19,360
Since you don't wish to be the Prince Consort,

215
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:21,639
then this princess shall...

216
00:11:25,519 --> 00:11:26,000
Shall what?

217
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:29,000
Then I'll just marry into your Ning household.

218
00:11:31,559 --> 00:11:32,720
As long as my dear Ning agrees,

219
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:34,000
I'm willing to be a concubine.

220
00:11:34,919 --> 00:11:35,360
I...

221
00:11:35,799 --> 00:11:36,840
Why are you doing this?

222
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:37,799
I don't care.

223
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:39,399
I've already said the words anyway.

224
00:11:39,759 --> 00:11:40,799
If you reject me,

225
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:42,440
how will this princess ever face anyone again?

226
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:54,440
Imperial Edict arriving!

227
00:11:57,679 --> 00:11:59,399
Ning Chen, receive the edict.

228
00:12:02,519 --> 00:12:04,039
By the Mandate of Heaven,

229
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:05,600
Xuandi decrees:

230
00:12:05,879 --> 00:12:08,000
Ning Chen, accomplished in both arts and arms,

231
00:12:08,399 --> 00:12:09,519
has rendered great service to the nation,

232
00:12:09,919 --> 00:12:11,000
remaining humble and composed.

233
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:12,639
We are deeply gratified.

234
00:12:13,039 --> 00:12:15,960
He is hereby granted the title of Carefree Marquis,

235
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:18,399
with a stipend of three thousand piculs,

236
00:12:18,639 --> 00:12:20,320
and granted a marquis estate.

237
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:25,080
Yet, while Ning Chen has ample courage,

238
00:12:25,440 --> 00:12:26,600
he lacks steadiness.

239
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:29,519
Men must wed, and women must marry.

240
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:34,600
Ninth Princess Huaian and he
are a perfect match.

241
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:36,480
We hereby bestow this marriage.

242
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:38,519
So decreed.

243
00:12:38,639 --> 00:12:39,200
Your child accepts the edict.

244
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:40,399
Your subject accepts the edict.

245
00:12:43,399 --> 00:12:43,960
My Lord Marquis.

246
00:12:44,200 --> 00:12:44,799
His Majesty

247
00:12:44,919 --> 00:12:46,600
also asked me to pass on a message.

248
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:47,759
No matter what you think,

249
00:12:47,919 --> 00:12:50,000
Huaian's been handed over to you anyway.

250
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:52,240
His Majesty also said,

251
00:12:52,519 --> 00:12:53,320
for a man,

252
00:12:53,480 --> 00:12:55,240
conquering the realm isn't much of a feat.

253
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:58,200
You must take good care
of every woman who loves you.

254
00:12:58,559 --> 00:13:00,120
Oh, and take care of your health.

255
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:02,559
Eat plenty of kidneys.

256
00:13:03,159 --> 00:13:03,720
Kidneys?

257
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:10,120
You're not the least bit embarrassed.

258
00:13:12,919 --> 00:13:13,720
And this is...?

259
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:15,960
Nanzhi.

260
00:13:19,440 --> 00:13:20,399
And this gentleman is...?

261
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:21,759
The Eunuch.

262
00:13:22,399 --> 00:13:23,320
Our ancestors are slightly related.

263
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:24,240
Have you ever thought,

264
00:13:24,679 --> 00:13:26,600
no wonder we look a bit alike.

265
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:27,639
A bit of family resemblance, right?

266
00:13:28,399 --> 00:13:29,559
We sure do. Call me Godfather.

267
00:13:30,519 --> 00:13:31,120
Wait, those two...

268
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:32,200
What are you doing over there?

269
00:13:37,559 --> 00:13:39,200
What, do you feel wronged?

270
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:43,000
Then I thank the Princess for her favor.

271
00:13:43,120 --> 00:13:46,200
I'll just have to grin and bear
having multiple wives.

272
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:48,919
The Old General has arrived!

273
00:14:05,559 --> 00:14:06,240
You old swindler!

274
00:14:07,919 --> 00:14:08,840
You're using the speedy legs.

275
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,080
You little brat.

276
00:14:12,480 --> 00:14:14,799
The speedy legs you gave me

277
00:14:14,919 --> 00:14:16,000
are truly fantastic.

278
00:14:16,399 --> 00:14:19,360
They make me feel like a withered tree
blooming in spring.

279
00:14:19,519 --> 00:14:21,159
I can go back to the battlefield again.

280
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:22,480
Oh, give it a rest.

281
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:23,720
With that third leg of yours,

282
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:24,879
just use it at home.

283
00:14:25,279 --> 00:14:26,440
Battlefield, my foot.

284
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:28,559
Even getting to the Music Bureau
wears you out, right?

285
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:31,360
Brat, there's much you don't know.

286
00:14:31,879 --> 00:14:34,080
I happen to have remarkable gifts.

287
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:41,519
Come here.

288
00:14:44,519 --> 00:14:45,120
Young Master.

289
00:14:45,679 --> 00:14:46,440
I heard

290
00:14:47,159 --> 00:14:48,159
that you kissed me.

291
00:14:48,759 --> 00:14:51,159
So you have to take responsibility for me.

292
00:14:51,759 --> 00:14:52,720
When did I kiss you?

293
00:14:53,080 --> 00:14:54,480
Here comes another one.

294
00:14:54,879 --> 00:14:55,320
I...

295
00:14:55,879 --> 00:14:56,360
I...

296
00:14:58,480 --> 00:14:59,279
You little brat.

297
00:14:59,559 --> 00:15:01,919
Xiaomei is now my goddaughter.

298
00:15:02,120 --> 00:15:02,679
From now on,

299
00:15:02,919 --> 00:15:05,120
you can't call me an old swindler anymore.

300
00:15:05,279 --> 00:15:06,480
You'll have to call me Godfather.

301
00:15:12,399 --> 00:15:12,879
Little sister.

302
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:14,399
From now on, I'm your second sister.

303
00:15:16,440 --> 00:15:17,120
Hello, second sister.

304
00:15:17,600 --> 00:15:18,480
I'm your eldest sister.

305
00:15:20,080 --> 00:15:20,600
Eldest sister.

306
00:15:21,200 --> 00:15:21,600
Then...

307
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:23,039
Then I...

308
00:15:23,159 --> 00:15:24,080
What do you mean, "I"?

309
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:27,080
You little brat.

310
00:15:27,200 --> 00:15:28,720
You're a lucky devil with the ladies.

311
00:15:30,200 --> 00:15:31,360
Commander Geng has arrived!

312
00:15:34,799 --> 00:15:35,879
Reporting to the Carefree Marquis.

313
00:15:36,159 --> 00:15:37,960
Wu Kingdom invades;
the Southern Frontier is in crisis.

314
00:15:38,360 --> 00:15:39,080
His Majesty orders you

315
00:15:39,320 --> 00:15:41,679
to lead the Divine Strategy Battalion
to the Southern Frontier at once.

316
00:16:54,919 --> 00:16:55,759
Third brother.

317
00:16:56,240 --> 00:16:57,399
Second brother.

318
00:17:17,440 --> 00:17:18,519
What are you going to do?

319
00:17:26,400 --> 00:17:27,119
Don't be afraid, don't be afraid.

320
00:17:27,319 --> 00:17:28,519
We're not bad people.

321
00:17:29,079 --> 00:17:30,880
I used to be just like you two.

322
00:17:31,599 --> 00:17:32,680
Without proper clothes,

323
00:17:33,039 --> 00:17:34,240
without enough to eat.

324
00:17:34,880 --> 00:17:36,160
But as men,

325
00:17:36,480 --> 00:17:37,279
you two remember,

326
00:17:37,759 --> 00:17:38,839
no matter when,

327
00:17:39,279 --> 00:17:40,880
you must keep your dignity.

328
00:17:41,039 --> 00:17:41,880
Keep your dignity.

329
00:17:42,039 --> 00:17:42,400
That's right.

330
00:17:43,400 --> 00:17:44,599
Here, cover up.

331
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:46,000
Take it, take it.

332
00:17:46,119 --> 00:17:46,440
Take it, take it.

333
00:17:46,440 --> 00:17:47,119
Cover yourself up.

334
00:17:47,240 --> 00:17:47,759
Don't catch a cold.

335
00:17:49,119 --> 00:17:49,480
Here.

336
00:17:49,839 --> 00:17:50,799
Give them some more buns to eat.

337
00:17:50,960 --> 00:17:51,839
Here, have a bun.

338
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:52,599
Come on, have a bun.

339
00:17:52,759 --> 00:17:53,599
Have a bun, brother.

340
00:17:53,839 --> 00:17:54,519
Eat up, come on.

341
00:17:57,440 --> 00:17:58,119
Thank you, benefactor.

342
00:17:58,359 --> 00:17:59,119
Thank you, benefactor.

343
00:17:59,240 --> 00:18:00,279
We used to be

344
00:18:00,519 --> 00:18:01,880
just as down-and-out as you two.

345
00:18:02,400 --> 00:18:03,480
You've got to believe in dreams.

346
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:05,480
What if they actually come true?

347
00:18:05,680 --> 00:18:06,119
That's right.

348
00:18:06,559 --> 00:18:08,960
You must build your dreams
with your own hands.

349
00:18:09,400 --> 00:18:11,640
Make your dreams come true
with your own hands.

350
00:18:11,799 --> 00:18:12,680
Yes.

351
00:18:13,279 --> 00:18:13,880
Thank you, benefactor.

352
00:18:14,319 --> 00:18:15,200
Thank you, benefactor.

353
00:18:15,680 --> 00:18:17,279
Back then, our benefactor

354
00:18:17,599 --> 00:18:18,759
told us the very same thing.

355
00:18:20,200 --> 00:18:21,160
What was his name again?

356
00:18:21,519 --> 00:18:23,000
His name was

357
00:18:23,240 --> 00:18:25,880
The Four Carefree Young Masters.
